WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.880 --> 00:00:03.080
OK, we're into their email.

2
00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.040
Well, this looks like she's been
 the victim of a sustained phishing attack.

3
00:00:09.320 --> 00:00:12.440
Hmm. I mean, they all appear
 to be from genuine companies,

4
00:00:12.440 --> 00:00:14.880
but I bet you a dozen
 doughnut's only one's legit.

5
00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.040
Have a look at the previews of the
emails and select the only genuine one.

6
00:00:20.640 --> 00:00:23.280
If you pick the wrong one,
 that'll lose us time.

7
00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:26.400
So make sure you read them all carefully.

